      • compareTo

        public int compareTo(Result candidate)
        When we have finished building our Results list, we need to sort the list by each Results score so that we can return the ranked list. Our list should be sorted in descending order (highest scores first).
        Specified by:
        compareTo in interface Comparable<Result>
        Parameters:
        candidate - Result being compared to 'this' Result
        Returns:
        -1 if this Result has a higher score, 0 if the same, 1 if score is lower.
